    Great questions! Let me answer both:

    1. YES - You can take the site down anytime! âœ…

    After publishing, you can unpublish/shut down your site whenever you want:

    • Go to the "Manage" tab in Publishing
    • Click "Shut Down"
    • Your site goes offline immediately

    Publishing is NOT permanent - you have full control! ðŸŽ›ï¸

    2. Let's open the Preview so you can check everything:

    Your site is running! Here's how to see it:

    Option A - Quick way:

    • Look for a browser/window icon in the top right of Replit
    • OR look for "Webview" or "Preview" tab
    • Click it to see your live site

    Option B - Manual way:

    • Click the "All tools" icon (grid icon) on the left sidebar
    • Select "Preview"
    • Your site will open

    Option C - Direct URL (works right now):

    • Open this in a new browser tab: https://workspace.phxbrandzall.repl.co
